CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 26, 2006

[Cite as 04/26/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-1967.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-0235. Olynyk v. Andrish.

Cuyahoga App. No. 86009, 2005-Ohio-6632. On review of order certifying a conflict. The court determines that no conflict exists. This cause is therefore dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Pfeifer, O’Connor and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Resnick, Lundberg Stratton and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent.
